author: NetworkChuck
description:
Stay connected from anywhere–even Cisco Live. See how we keep our studio online with Twingate :https://ntck.co/twingate_ciscolive2025 

I haven’t been back to Cisco Live since 2019. But this year, I brought my entire team. The largest networking conference in the world, 22,000 people all in one place, talking about networking. But this year…felt different. There was a heaviness in the air, all because of one thing: AI.

In this video, I’m taking you with me to Cisco Live 2025. I’ll show you who I met, and how my experience was different this year. Then, we’re going to rewind, and find out how this conference got started in the first place, and how it’s changed over the years, all the way up to AI: the biggest shift networking has seen in decades.
